    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Generate a high-converting BOFU blog post for this topic:\n\n{{ $json.selectedTopic }}\n\nMANDATORY STRUCTURE (strict compliance required):\n\n1. H1: Evergreen headline (clear, location-specific for Temecula area including Temecula, Temecula Wine Country, De Luz, Meadowview, Murrieta, Winchester, Menifee, La Cresta, decision-stage optimized)\n2. Bold Opening Question: Engaging, emotionally compelling, buyer/seller intent\n3. SEO Meta Description: 140-160 characters, click-optimized, contains primary keyword\n4. Authority Positioning Section: Establish Temecula area real estate expertise, data-backed, local market knowledge\n5. Deep Structured Sections: Clear H2/H3 hierarchy, data-driven insights, neighborhood-level references (Temecula Wine Country, De Luz, Meadowview, Murrieta, Winchester, Menifee, La Cresta), pricing trends, buyer/seller guidance, risk considerations, market timing analysis\n6. FAQ Section: 3-5 highly relevant BOFU questions, schema-friendly formatting\n7. Strong Closing: Conversion-oriented, encourage next step, trust-building\n8. Author Bio: Local expert positioning, credibility reinforcement\n\nREQUIREMENTS:\n- 800-1200 words\n- SEO optimized (on-page best practices)\n- GEO optimized (Temecula area location-rich signals)\n- Authoritative but accessible tone\n- Decision-stage reader focus\n- Data-driven, avoid fluff\n- Unique insights\n- Natural internal linking placeholders [LINK: anchor text]\n\nReturn complete HTML-formatted content with proper heading tags.",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are an elite NYC real estate content writer and SEO specialist. You create BOFU content that converts browsers into buyers and sellers. Your writing is authoritative, data-driven, locally relevant, and optimized for both search engines and human decision-makers. You NEVER deviate from the mandatory structure. Every piece includes specific NYC neighborhoods, current market data, and actionable guidance."
        }
      },
